    "elemenduo": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "caption": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "First Collection",
            "text_style": "caption-with-letter-spacing",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Elemenduo — twelve characters, born of earth and sky.",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our first collection draws from a story full of mythological elements. Twelve main characters, born from the marriage of earth and sky, lend their names to the pieces — <em>Flos, Solis, Glacies, Luminis, Maris, Luna, Petra, Stellata, Tempestas, Terra</em>. Seym Glass Studio products remind people of the beauty of nature by bringing unique fragments of these elements into living spaces.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["caption", "heading", "text"],
      "settings": {
