          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "Founder's Note",
            "text_style": "caption-with-letter-spacing",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "A quieter way of making.",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We choose character over perfection. Identity over trend. Each piece carries its own presence — never shouting, yet never ignored. We do not imitate. We aim not for the eye, but for the mind. What we make is not ornament. It is statement.</p><p><em>This is not glass as you know it. This is Seym.</em></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
